          "content": "Is it appropriate to call someone honey?\nIt can be extremely off-putting—especially if the person has ever been in a situation where terms like “honey” or “dear” have been used in a demeaning way to make them feel less-than in a past job or relationship. This is why it's always better to refer to customers in a consistent and respectful manner."
